===Verb===
{{nl-verb}}

# {{lb|nl|copulative}} to [[become]]; to [[get]]; to [[grow]]; to [[turn]]
#: {{ux|nl|Zij wilde altijd al lerares '''worden'''.|She always wanted to become a teacher.|inline=1}}
#: {{ux|nl|Mijn broer '''wordt''' vandaag twintig.|My brother is turning twenty today.|inline=1}} 
# {{lb|nl|transitive|auxiliary}} {{n-g|Used to form the [[imperfect tense]] of the [[passive voice]], together with a [[past participle]].}}
